{"tid":1643263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得香港就係風水講嘅真龍?","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T14:00:14.000Z","uid":29666,"like":1018,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"5a4f37c475c5a2bac9d3fa2e603971c7c28db561","tid":1643263,"uid":29666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"今次事件重新凝聚左香港人抗衡共產黨嘅侵略。<br />\n以過往記錄社會運動好快就會完結， 但今次可以發酵到咁大， 甚至去到可以動搖到中共政權。<br />\n<br />\n事件發展左一個月，就有721 事件，然後成個形勢唔同晒。<br />\n<br />\n呢排運動開始膠著，呢幾日又有NBA事件，加試強國網民助攻，令到本身唔係好關心政治嘅美國人都開始留意香港事件。 頭先上reddit 睇，10個有6個post都係講香港<br />\n<br />\n感覺香港已經重新成為國際城市，成為世界焦點<br />\n<br />\n星加坡努力左好耐想取代香港，但今次事件令香港又重新變成世界城市，得到全球支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感覺我哋就係被選中嘅一代<br />\n<br />\n光復香港就好似令香港重新獲得昔日嘅光輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2319cd401c152d88aa12b12289b1e758a74a8a","tid":1643263,"uid":29666,"like":219,"dislike":0,"score":219,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:08:59.000Z","msg":"命中注定香港就係東方之珠"},{"pid":"043862031dc03e3fea6bff77bc209a0f8f653e93","tid":1643263,"uid":182519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"[行動post][招兵]想唔想見證支爆？國際大型文宣#WhatIfTheyOwnIt上線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1642404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1642404</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"881d5522a49cc1647354ed5fdeb2aef5b12ff75d","tid":1643263,"uid":113155,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:20:02.000Z","msg":"新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428218bf98e490eade0944f197c2aee4d2cf4984","tid":1643263,"uid":22360,"like":206,"dislike":3,"score":203,"quote":{"pid":"881d5522a49cc1647354ed5fdeb2aef5b12ff75d","tid":1643263,"uid":113155,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:20:02.000Z","msg":"新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":